IS NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

26:34.714 --> 26:36.345
HE'S A MATERIAL WITNESS
IN A MURDER,

26:36.345 --> 26:37.977
POSSIBLY EVEN A SUSPECT.

26:37.977 --> 26:39.979
