ABOUT THE CODE CIVIL.

26:39.979 --> 26:41.600
DR. PIERCE
HAS THE RIGHT TO COUNCIL.

26:41.600 --> 26:43.222
MONSIEUR,
UNLESS YOU ARE CERTIFIED

26:43.222 --> 26:45.224
TO PRACTICE LAW
IN THIS COUNTRY,

26:45.224 --> 26:46.856
YOU CAN'T SEE HIM.
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:46.856 --> 26:49.488
LISTEN, DETECTIVE,
I'M A COP, TOO, ALL RIGHT?

26:49.488 --> 26:51.320
