ON THE WAY HOME.

28:02.802 --> 28:04.643
Y-YOU'RE -- YOU'RE NOT -- YOU'RE
NOT PUTTING ME ON A PLANE.

28:04.643 --> 28:06.265
WE'RE TAKING YOU HOME HERE,
TO MIRANDA'S.

28:06.265 --> 28:09.729
