IT WAS EASY MONEY.

32:25.524 --> 32:27.866
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]
Drexler: AGENT MORETTI?

32:27.866 --> 32:29.568
AGENT DREXLER.

32:29.568 --> 32:31.660
