REVOKE HIS SECURITY CLEARANCE.

32:45.214 --> 32:47.386
YEAH, WELL, I CAN'T LEAVE.
I DON'T HAVE A...

32:47.386 --> 32:50.549
PASSPORT.
HOT OFF THE PRESS.

32:50.549 --> 32:52.471
HAVE A SAFE FLIGHT.

32:56.595 --> 33:00.519
