ACTUALLY WENT THROUGH WITH IT.

33:00.519 --> 33:03.692
WELL, I-I TRIED TO WARN YOU.
[ GROANS ]

33:03.692 --> 33:06.105
THE PHONE'S BEEN RINGING
OFF THE HOOK ALL MORNING.

33:06.105 --> 33:08.657
DONORS ARE THREATENING
TO PULL THEIR MONEY.

33:08.657 --> 33:10.409
THE A.C.L.U.
IS BREATHING DOWN MY NECK.

33:10.409 --> 33:12.611
