STUDENTS ARE PLANNING
A PROTEST RALLY LATER.

33:12.611 --> 33:15.534
THIS IS A DISASTER.
WHAT DID YOU EXPECT?

33:15.534 --> 33:18.707
WE HAVE TO FIX THIS NOW.

33:18.707 --> 33:21.380
