I'D REALLY APPRECIATE

38:25.554 --> 38:26.925
IF YOU COULD KEEP ME UPDATED

38:26.925 --> 38:28.016
ON THE PROGRESS
OF THE INVESTIGATION.

38:28.016 --> 38:30.018
THANK YOU.

38:30.018 --> 38:32.641
SOME NEWS ON SERGE,
COURTESY OF AGENT DREXLER.

38:32.641 --> 38:35.774
FRENCH INTELLIGENCE BELIEVES
HE'S AN IRANIAN DOUBLE AGENT.

38:35.774 --> 38:37.486
[ SCOFFS ]

38:37.486 --> 38:39.237
LOOKS LIKE YOU WERE RIGHT,
DANIEL.

38:39.237 --> 38:41.530
SERGE MUST HAVE
MASTERMINDED THE ENTIRE THING.

38:41.530 --> 38:44.533
YEAH. UNLESS HE DIDN'T.

38:44.533 --> 38:45.994
I GUESS
ONE OF THE CHINESE GUYS

38:45.994 --> 38:47.496
COULD HAVE BEEN
THE BRAIN TRUST,

38:47.496 --> 38:49.618
