38:52.371 --> 38:54.212
MAX.

38:56.294 --> 38:58.126
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

39:01.510 --> 39:05.634
WE'RE IN PARIS.

39:05.634 --> 39:08.346
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

39:08.346 --> 39:09.848
LEWICKI?
MAX: Doc.

39:09.848 --> 39:11.390
Hey, hey, no, no.
Don't hang up. Don't hang up.

39:11.390 --> 39:13.231
I GOT AN UPDATE ON THAT THING
THAT WE TALKED ABOUT.

39:13.231 --> 39:14.853
NOT ONLY IS THE CHANCELLOR

39:14.853 --> 39:16.855
OFFERING TO REINSTATE YOU
AS A TEACHER --

39:16.855 --> 39:19.478
NO QUESTIONS ASKED,
NO APOLOGY --

39:19.478 --> 39:23.321
HE'S GIVING YOU A 35% RAISE,
