WITH A PARKING SPOT?

39:27.155 --> 39:28.657
Doc, please.

39:28.657 --> 39:31.490
OKAY. LOOK,
YOU'VE GOT TO COME BACK, OKAY?

39:31.490 --> 39:33.792
IT'S NOT THE SAME HERE
WITHOUT YOU.

39:33.792 --> 39:35.754
[ CHUCKLES ]
OH, I KNEW IT.

39:35.754 --> 39:37.165
I KNEW THAT WEASEL,
KINNEY,

39:37.165 --> 39:38.997
WOULD COME CRAWLING BACK
ON HIS HANDS AND KNEES.

39:38.997 --> 39:42.421
YOU KNOW WHAT?
LET HIM SQUIRM FOR A WHILE.

39:42.421 --> 39:45.003
AND THEN ACCEPT.

39:45.003 --> 39:47.215
YES!

39:47.215 --> 39:50.058
DOC, WHEN YOU GET BACK,
YOU AND ME,

39:50.058 --> 39:51.680
WE OUGHT TO HANG OUT MORE,
OKAY?

39:51.680 --> 39:53.682
