BE ABLE TO TALK ABOUT ANYTHING.

39:53.682 --> 39:55.894
YOU AND ME, GUY TO GUY.
HEY, MAYBE WE CAN EVEN, LIKE,

39:55.894 --> 39:58.106
YOU KNOW -- DOC?
[ Tone sounds ]

